aa(lp52
VThat last word is a very human thing to do, to dehumanize the people we hurt.
p53
aVIt's because we want to destroy people but not feel bad about it.
p54
aVImagine if this was an actual court,
p55
aVand the accused was in the dark, begging for another chance,
p56
aVand the jury was yelling out,
p57
aV"Bored! Sociopath!"
p58
aV(Laughter)
