VYou know, when we watch courtroom dramas, we tend to identify
p61
aVwith the kindhearted defense attorney,
p62
aVbut give us the power, and we become like hanging judges.
p63
aa(lp64
VPower shifts fast.
p65
aVWe were getting Jonah because he was perceived to have misused his privilege,
p66
aVbut Jonah was on the floor then, and we were still kicking,
p67
aVand congratulating ourselves for punching up.
p68
aVAnd it began to feel weird and empty when there wasn't a powerful person
p69
aVwho had misused their privilege that we could get.
