VWhat had happened is that one of her 170 followers had sent the Tweet
p103
aVto a Gawker journalist, and he retweeted it to his 15,000 followers:
p104
aV[And now, a funny holiday joke from IAC's PR boss]
p105
aVAnd then it was like a bolt of lightning.
p106
aVA few weeks later, I talked to the Gawker journalist.
p107
aVI emailed him and asked him how it felt, and he said, "It felt delicious."
p108
aVAnd then he said, "But I'm sure she's fine."
