aa(lp110
VBut she wasn't fine, because while she slept,
p111
aVTwitter took control of her life and dismantled it piece by piece.
p112
aVFirst there were the philanthropists:
p113
aV[If @JustineSacco's unfortunate words ... bother you,
p114
aVjoin me in supporting @CARE's work in Africa.]
