aVIn fact, when I met Justine a couple of weeks later in a bar,
p134
aVshe was just crushed,
p135
aVand I asked her to explain the joke,
p136
aVand she said, "Living in America puts us in a bit of a bubble
p137
aVwhen it comes to what is going on in the Third World.
p138
aVI was making of fun of that bubble."
