aa(lp281
VAnd I think back on the early days of Twitter,
p282
aVwhen people would admit shameful secrets about themselves,
p283
aVand other people would say, "Oh my God, I'm exactly the same."
p284
aVThese days, the hunt is on for people's shameful secrets.
p285
aVYou can lead a good, ethical life,
p286
aVbut some bad phraseology in a Tweet can overwhelm it all,
p287
aVbecome a clue to your secret inner evil.
